data.description: WOW! Seller will pay 14K towards buyer's closing cost!!* Spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers a generous living space with high ceilings that create an open & airy atmosphere. The kitchen island is perfect for meal prep and gatherings. Spacious pantry, lazy-susan for additional storage & newer countertops! All appliances match. Popular farm style sink! All bedrooms are upstairs and conveniently, the nice sized laundry is upstairs too! Ceiling fans in all the rooms! Primary bedroom features walk in closet. Separate garden tub & shower!  The 2-car garage offers plenty of storage space & private parking. Located in a prime Phoenix neighborhood close to shopping & transportation! Home warranty being offered! Community pool is close by! Gated community! Make this HOME today!
